            <h2>Essential Packing List for University Freshmen</h2>
            <p>Preparing for university involves packing all the essentials to ensure a smooth transition. 
                <br> Start with the basics: bedding, including sheets, pillows, and a comforter; toiletries like soap, shampoo, and a toothbrush; and clothing appropriate for the climate. 
                <br> Don’t forget important documents such as your ID, admission letter, and financial information. 
                <br> Academic supplies like notebooks, pens, a laptop, and textbooks are crucial. Kitchen items, if you’re cooking, include utensils, pots, and pans. 
                <br> Consider comfort items like photos, decorations, and a desk lamp to make your space feel like home. 
                <br> Lastly, bring some basic cleaning supplies to keep your room tidy. 
               <br> Packing these essentials will help you start university life on the right foot.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modal8" class="modal">
